{"id":129108,"type":6,"name":"盛世仁傑","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/33/4f/129108_tTDtd.jpg","summary":"　　狄仁杰官拜宰相，有青天之名，不少冤狱苦主都来跪拜恳求，请宰相为他们伸冤翻案。狄仁杰也尽心竭力查，以还苦主一个公道。京城接二连三发生神秘疑案，狄仁杰百思不得其解，原来这个案件背后都由武则天的侄子武承嗣主使，而他的目标更直指太子之位，实行要把李家的唐氏天下，落入武氏手中。狄仁杰面对着这些盘根错节的疑案，应如何落幕？又如何替苦主洗雪冤情？","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>盛世仁杰</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>星期一至五 20:30－21:30</li><li><span>编剧: </span>林少枝、陳志強、<a href=\"/person/16672\">賈偉南</a>、<a href=\"/person/17053\">冼翠貞</a>、關炳洪、黎家明</li><li><span>监制: </span><a href=\"/person/17541\">梁材遠</a></li><li><span>编审: </span><a href=\"/person/16672\">賈偉南</a></li><li><span>主题歌演出: </span><a href=\"/person/17977\">張敬軒</a>《定局》</li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/17472\">鄭則士</a>、<a href=\"/person/16508\">陳錦鴻</a>、<a href=\"/person/16812\">郭羨妮</a>、<a href=\"/person/17107\">廖碧兒</a>、<a href=\"/person/16437\">黎耀祥</a>、<a href=\"/person/16502\">陳秀珠</a>、<a href=\"/person/17287\">唐寧</a>、<a href=\"/person/16422\">李香琴</a>、<a href=\"/person/17051\">曹永廉</a>、<a href=\"/person/17154\">李天翔</a></li><li><span>配角: </span><a href=\"/person/26270\">馮素波</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>The Greatness Of A Hero</li><li><span>集数: </span>20</li><li><span>开始: </span>2012-04-02</li><li><span>结束: </span>2012-04-27</li><li><span>类型: </span>古裝宮廷</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>香港</li><li><span>电视台: </span>TVB</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>programme.tvb.com/drama/thegreatnessofahero</li><li><span>编导: </span>歐耀興、林鳳玲、冼燕芳、朱禮和</li><li><span>助理编导: </span>李鳳明、張婉婷、黃立天、杜文鋒、溫發良、邱銘</li><li><span>制作年份: </span>2008年1－4月</li><li><span>制作统筹: </span>黃青</li>","eps":[{"id":506918,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/506918","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":506919,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/506919","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":506920,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/506920","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status"